  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Implementation Lead",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Delivery Leadership</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead the end-to-end implementation of eBao Gemini / InsureMO modules (Policy Admin, Claims, Product Engine, API Integration).</li>\n  <li>Review and validate all functional and technical deliverables from the offshore team before client submission.</li>\n  <li>Participate in design and configuration workshops; guide the offshore team in applying best practices from prior eBao projects.</li>\n  <li>Manage daily interaction with clients business, IT, and vendor teams to ensure alignment and quality.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Solution &amp; Configuration Expertise</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Be hands-on with product configuration, workflows, and rule setup in eBao (Gemini/InsureMO).</li>\n  <li>Understand how to manage customer configurations, environments, and test data.</li>\n  <li>Build reusable configuration templates, documentation, and checklists to accelerate the next projects.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Capability Development</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Mentor the offshore team in areas such as:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Product configuration &amp; parameterization</li>\n  <li>InsureMO API exposure &amp; orchestration</li>\n  <li>Test case design &amp; defect triage</li>\n  <li>Deployment &amp; environment management</li>\n  <li>Define skill maturity models for BAs, testers, and configurators to track progress toward implementation-certified level.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Client &amp; Vendor Coordination</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Serve as technical and functional spokesperson during client workshops and vendor syncs (with eBaoTech).</li>\n  <li>Review solution design and implementation plans together with eBao consultants.</li>\n  <li>Escalate and resolve issues proactively across client, vendor, and FPT teams.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>CoE Framework Establishment</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Co-define COE structure, process standards, and documentation.</li>\n  <li>Create a knowledge base (configuration guide, testing templates, deployment standards) for reuse.</li>\n  <li>Support internal training and certification roadmaps with eBaoTech.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5+ years implementing eBaoTech solutions (Gemini / InsureMO / Policy Admin / Claims / Billing). Experience in both configuration and integration.</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of Life / General / Health insurance workflows: policy, claims, endorsements, billing.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with eBao configuration console, APIs, JSON mapping, middleware/integration (InsureMO), SQL, and cloud environments.</li>\n  <li>Experience leading at least 23 end-to-end eBao implementations (insurer or partner side).</li>\n  <li>Strong stakeholder management, mentoring capability, and ability to handle ambiguity in early-stage COE setup.</li>\n  <li>eBao InsureMO Certified Implementation Professional, Agile/Scrum Master, ISTQB (for QA background).</li>\n</ul>",
